190
00:22:52,279 --> 00:22:55,740
I put on one more act by torturing you to gain the enemy's confidence.

191
00:22:55,740 --> 00:22:59,000
It is so that you can easily get into the Mountain and Sea gang.

192
00:22:59,700 --> 00:23:03,180
However, when that time comes, whether you live or die, it will all depend on you.

193
00:23:03,700 --> 00:23:07,680
You should take good care of yourself.

194
00:23:11,060 --> 00:23:14,160
Do you know what the biggest difference between us is?

195
00:23:16,080 --> 00:23:18,260
We both have hatred.

196
00:23:18,260 --> 00:23:20,340
However, I want to be human

197
00:23:21,440 --> 00:23:23,480
but you'd rather be a ghost.

198
00:23:28,900 --> 00:23:30,830
So now,

199
00:23:32,490 --> 00:23:35,040
