202
00:26:41,480 --> 00:26:44,960
Who did you hear that from? Such a jealous man!

203
00:26:44,960 --> 00:26:48,579
I am her husband and I haven't even had the first night with her.

204
00:26:48,579 --> 00:26:52,579
How can you let that guy take advantage of her? I can't tolerate it.

205
00:26:55,040 --> 00:26:56,900
If you can carry her, then you do it.

206
00:26:58,100 --> 00:27:02,899
Fine then! Let me, the best assassin who killed Liu Song, carry you.

207
00:27:02,899 --> 00:27:05,359
How is it, Darling? Isn't it honorable?

208
00:27:10,200 --> 00:27:12,979
- Did you do that on purpose?
- Not at all!

209
00:27:12,979 --> 00:27:16,840
- You totally did that on purpose!
- Really, I didn't!

210
00:27:16,840 --> 00:27:19,240
- Mo Lin!
- I didn't!

211
00:27:19,240 --> 00:27:22,580
- Stop right there!
- Darling, I didn't.

212
00:27:22,580 --> 00:27:23,710
You did it on purpose.

213
00:27:23,710 --> 00:27:25,740
- I didn't.
- Stop running!

214
00:27:25,740 --> 00:27:28,279
Mo Lin, you did it on purpose.

215
00:27:28,279 --> 00:27:30,280
Darling.

216
00:27:39,600 --> 00:27:41,600
Lu Ping.

217
00:27:45,360 --> 00:27:47,920
Eldest Senior, can't you not lean on me?

218
