239
00:29:50,260 --> 00:29:54,600
Yes! One is major and the other is minor.

240
00:29:54,600 --> 00:29:56,910
One is bright and the other is dark.

241
00:29:56,910 --> 00:30:02,760
You chose to be an official, then I will choose to stay in the pugilist world.

242
00:30:05,060 --> 00:30:07,400
Fighting for the ordinary people,

243
00:30:09,280 --> 00:30:11,440
